You will be able to purchase a BTCBULLDOG NFT directly on this website with Ethereum (ETH) by using the MetaMask extension.

What is the mint price of BTCBULLDOG NFT ?

Our Pre-Sale mint price is 0.05 ETH + gas fees per NFT. Our Whitelisted members will be allowed to mint two NFTs.

How long after minting will my NFT be revealed?

The reveal will be instant.
